OL,3,CYears of accounting blunders leave
OL,4,Cpolice force with #65m blackhole
OL,6,FSouth Yorkshire Police says there will
OL,7,Fbe an inevitable impact on services
OL,8,Fafter what it called a "significant
OL,9,Ferror" in accounting led to the
OL,10,Fdiscovery of a #65million black hole
OL,11,Fin its budget.
OL,13,FOn Friday, 27 September, the force and
OL,14,Fthe South Yorkshire Mayor Oliver
OL,15,FCoppard both released statements
OL,16,Frevealing that years of unfinanced
OL,17,Fspending on essential equipment
OL,18,Fincluding kit for officers, vehicles
OL,19,Fand IT gear and services had gone
OL,20,Funnoticed.
