OL,3,CYears of accounting blunders leave
OL,4,Cpolice force with #65m blackhole
OL,6,FMr Coppard said: "These problems would
OL,7,Fappear to represent a fundamental
OL,8,Ferror in accounting practices in the
OL,9,Foffice of the former PCC (police and
OL,10,Fcrime commissioner).
OL,12,F"Those mistakes were missed by
OL,13,Fexternal and internal checks.
OL,15,F"I have now instructed my office to
OL,16,Fbring in an external team to
OL,17,Findependently look at the processes
OL,18,Fthat allowed those mistakes to go
OL,19,Fundetected for five years."
