OL,3,CYears of accounting blunders leave
OL,4,Cpolice force with #65m blackhole
OL,6,FThe force is now seeking financial
OL,7,Fsupport from the government.
OL,9,FChief Constable Lauren Poultney said
OL,10,Fshe felt "great disappointment" at the
OL,11,Fnews and "the impact this will have on
OL,12,Fthe financial stability of South
OL,13,FYorkshire Police".
OL,15,F'There will of course be challenges'
