OL,3,CYears of accounting blunders leave
OL,4,Cpolice force with #65m blackhole
OL,6,FShe added that the force had savings
OL,7,Fand reserves which would mitigate the
OL,8,Fimpact of the problem, but "this is
OL,9,Fnot how we would seek to manage our
OL,10,Ffinances and it will, of course, have
OL,11,Fimpacts on the service we deliver".
OL,13,F"I have that assurance and feel
OL,14,Fconfident through working together and
OL,15,Fwith the support of the Home Office we
OL,16,Fwill be able to stabilise the budget
OL,17,Fand protect the services we offer,"
OL,18,Fshe said.
