OL,4,Cpolice force with #65m blackhole
OL,6,F"That said, there will of course be
OL,7,Fchallenges ahead as we work through
OL,8,Fthis.
OL,10,F"I have informed the workforce of this
OL,11,Ferror this morning and will do all I
OL,12,Fcan to offer them appropriate
OL,13,Freassurance so they can continue to
OL,14,Ffocus on the task ahead."
OL,16,FMr Coppard said the error came to
OL,17,Flight after the responsibilities for
OL,18,Fbudget oversight transferred from the
OL,19,Fformer office of the police and crime
OL,20,Fcommissioner to the mayor's office in
OL,21,FMay.
