OL,3,CYears of accounting blunders leave
OL,4,Cpolice force with #65m blackhole
OL,6,FHe said #16m of spending already made
OL,7,Fhad not been accounted for, along with
OL,8,F#49m of future spending commitments.
OL,10,FThe force said it would "do everything
OL,11,Fwe can" to protect services but it was
OL,12,F"too soon to say" if jobs would be
OL,13,Faffected.
OL,15,FLast year South Yorkshire Police had a
OL,16,Fbudget of #326m, of which 74% came
OL,17,Ffrom the government. The rest was paid
OL,18,Ffor through council tax.
